<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.8">
<l>kāṭṭinī karantumiḻu nilanīrtī vicumpukā</l>
<l>līṭṭinī vaittamaitta vimaiyōrvāḻ taṉimuṭṭaik</l>
<l>kōṭṭaiyiṉil kaḻitteṉaiyuṉ koḻuñcōti yuyarattu</l>
<l>kūṭṭariya tiruvaṭikka ḷeññāṉṟuṅ kūṭṭutiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having removed me from the fort</l>
<l>of the solitary egg where live the unblinking ones whom you placed [there and] created, ammassing</l>
<l>the earth you had swallowed, having shown [and] hidden [yourself?], the water, fire, sky [and] wind,</l>
<l>may you united me forever with [your] sacred feet that are difficult to unite with,</l>
	<l>in the loftiness of your rich light.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
